definitions.definition: A sensitive elongated erectile sex organ at the anterior part of the vulva in female humans and other mammals.
examples: She complains that her boyfriend can't find her clitoris .

definitions.definition: A similar erectile sexual organ present in the cloacas of female amniotes .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A sensitive elongated erectile sex organ at the anterior part of the vulva in female humans and other mammals. [from 17th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( zoology ) A similar erectile sexual organ present in the cloacas of female amniotes .
